# -- optional (for the sake of time to run AnnotateLanguage): 
mydf2 = mydf.sample(n = 100)
# -- end optional
mydf3 = ao3_functions.AnnotateLanguage(mydf2)
mydf4 = ao3_functions.CorrectLanguage(mydf3)
